  "prompt": "What is entrepreneurial passion?",
  "response": "Entrepreneurial passion is a deep, intense emotional commitment and enthusiasm towards entrepreneurial activities, goals, and ventures. It involves:\n\n1. Key characteristics:\n- Strong intrinsic motivation\n- Emotional investment in business pursuits\n- High levels of personal energy and dedication\n- Persistent commitment to entrepreneurial goals\n\n2. Components:\n- Cognitive passion (thinking about the venture)\n- Affective passion (emotional attachment)\n- Behavioral passion (active engagement)\n\n3. Psychological aspects:\n- Identity-driven motivation\n- Sense of personal fulfillment\n- Willingness to overcome challenges\n- Strong belief in one's business idea\n\n4. Benefits:\n- Increased resilience\n- Enhanced creativity\n- Better problem-solving skills\n- Improved decision-making\n- Greater likelihood of business success\n\n5. Sources of entrepreneurial passion:\n- Personal interests\n- Desire for innovation\n- Solving societal problems\n- Financial independence\n- Personal growth\n- Autonomy\n\n6. Impact on performance:\n- Higher commitment\n- More effective resource allocation\n- Increased likelihood of pursuing opportunities\n- Greater persistence during difficulties\n\nEntrepreneurial passion is a complex psychological construct that drives entrepreneurs to pursue and develop their business ventures with enthusiasm and dedication.",
